        <div class="section" id="section1">
            <div id="about-header" class="wow slideInLeft" data-wow-duration="0.7s">
              <h3 id="about-title">We are Code The South</h3>
            </div>
            <div id="about-inner-section" class="wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
              <p class="get-involved-p" id="about-p">A 501(c)(3) non-governmental organization formed to bring 21st century technology to the citizen-community experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden-xs about-purpose wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
              <h3 id="purpose-title">Our Purpose:</h3>
              <div class="row" id="about-row-1">
                <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-2 col-xs-4 purpose-item-format item-curved-reverse">
                  <p class="purpose-item-p">Encourage and support development of public and private innovation in the field of civic technologies.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-2 col-xs-4 purpose-item-format item-oval">
                  <p class="purpose-item-p">Promote effective and efficient technologies for civic interaction.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-2 col-xs-4 purpose-item-format item-curved">
                  <p class="purpose-item-p">Inform area residents of metro government data sources.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="row" id="about-row-2">
                <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-2 col-xs-4 purpose-item-format item-curved">
                  <p class="purpose-item-p">Empower citizen influence by working with public policy makers to expand and enhance open data standards.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-2 col-xs-4 purpose-item-format item-oval">
                  <p class="purpose-item-p">Provide educational opportunity to those wishing to learn about application design and implementation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-2 col-xs-4 purpose-item-format item-curved-reverse">
                  <p class="purpose-item-p">Garner resources for and to maintain and sustain viability of Code The South.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="visible-xs about-purpose">
              <h3 id="purpose-title" class="wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Our Purpose:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li class="wow fadeIn purpose-item-li" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Encourage and support development of public and private innovation in the field of civic technologies.</li>
                <li class="wow fadeIn purpose-item-li" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Promote effective and efficient technologies for civic interaction.</li>
                <li class="wow fadeIn purpose-item-li" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Inform area residents of metro government data sources.</li>
                <li class="wow fadeIn purpose-item-li" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Empower citizen influence by working with public policy makers to expand and enhance open data standards.</li>
                <li class="wow fadeIn purpose-item-li" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Provide educational opportunity to those wishing to learn about application design and implementation.</li>
                <li class="wow fadeIn purpose-item-li" data-wow-delay="0.5s">Garner resources for and to maintain and sustain viability of Code The South.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section" id="section2">
    		<div class="container-fluid get-involved-buffer">
    			<div class="row">
    				<div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
    					<h2 class="get-involved-header">Do you want to get involved?</h2>
      					<p class="get-involved-p">Join a group that fits your expertise.</p>
    					<hr class="double-style">
    				</div>
    			</div>
    		</div>
    		<div class="container">
    			<div class="row row-top-buffer">
    				<div class="col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-3 col-xs-6 text-center">
    					<div class="service-box">
    						<i class="fa fa-4x fa-group wow bounceIn text-primary"></i>
    						<h3 class="group-title">Community Member</h3>
    						<p class="text-muted">Writer, artist, organizer, storyteller or social media coordinator, we need you! Help organize meetings, steer committees or coordinate projects. Simply fill out the
                  <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1wkOoGgLyuDzO6MKjsB8yZhH1U1lfV5KGqJ9HWtLS6pA/edit?usp=drive_web" target="_blank">committee candidate form</a>.</p>
    					</div>
    				</div>
    				<div class="col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-3 col-xs-6 text-center">
    					<div class="service-box">
    						<i class="fa fa-4x fa-keyboard-o wow bounceIn text-primary"></i>
    						<h3 class="group-title">Software Developer</h3>
    						<p class="text-muted">Can you write code? Help us build apps to make the future better. Check out our
                  <a href="https://github.com/codeforhuntsville" target="_blank">GitHub</a> page to help.</p>
    					</div>
    				</div>
				</div>
			</div>
    		<div class="container">
    			<div class="row row-bottom-buffer">
    				<div class="col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-3 col-xs-6 text-center">
    					<div class="service-box">
    						<i class="fa fa-4x fa-recycle wow bounceIn text-primary" data-wow-delay=".2s"></i>
    						<h3 class="group-title">Nonprofit Agency</h3>
    						<p class="text-muted">We support nonprofit agencies! If you are involved with an NGO or nonprofit organization please contact us.</p>
    					</div>
    				</div>
    				<div class="col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-3 col-xs-6 text-center">
    					<div class="service-box">
    						<i class="fa fa-4x fa-newspaper-o wow bounceIn text-primary" data-wow-delay=".2s"></i>
    						<h3 class="group-title">Local Government Worker</h3>
    						<p class="text-muted">We need contacts to help us form new projects. Become a liaison for CodeTheSouth.</p>
    					</div>
    				</div>
    			</div>
    		</div>
        </div>
        <div class="section" id="section3">
		<div class="row" style=" style="margin-right:0; margin-left: 0;"">
            <div class="contact-us-top">
              <h1>Contact us, join the mailing list, or submit an idea!</h1>
            </div>
			</div>
		<div class="row"  style="margin-right:0; margin-left: 0; max-width:100%;">
            <div class="container-fluid">
              <div class="col-md-offset-4 col-md-4 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
                <form id="input-form">
                  <div class="form-group" id="email-form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Email address</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="inputEmail" placeholder="Email">
                  </div>
                  <label for="message">Message</label>
                  <textarea class="form-control" id="inputMessage" cols="30" rows="6"></textarea>
                  <br>
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn-block" id="contact-us-button">Submit</button>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
			</div>
          	<div class="row contact-us-footer" style="margin-right:0; margin-left: 0;">
              <div class="contact-us-bot">
      					<div class="col-md-offset-4 col-md-1 col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-2 socialmedia">
      						<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/code4huntsville" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-4x fa-facebook wow bounceIn" data-wow-delay=".2s"></i></a>
      					</div>
      					<div class="col-md-1 col-xs-2 socialmedia">
      						<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/follow?screen_name=code4huntsville" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-4x fa-twitter wow bounceIn"></i></a>
      					</div>
      					<div class="col-md-1 col-xs-2 socialmedia">
      						<a href="https://github.com/codeforhuntsville" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-4x fa-github wow bounceIn"></i></a>
      					</div>
      					<div class="col-md-1 col-xs-2 socialmedia">
      						<a href="https://codeforhuntsville.slack.com" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-4x fa-slack wow bounceIn" data-wow-delay=".2s"></i></a>
      					</div>
              </div>
